Revision history for Perl extension XML::DOM::BagOfTricks.

0.01  Thu Dec  9 18:06:10 2004
	- original version; created by h2xs 1.23 with options
		-X XML::DOM::BagOfTricks
        - created original module based on XML::Xerces::BagOfTricks
0.02  Wed Dec 22 2004
	- Modified API changing get to create where ambiguous
	- Added new methods based on XML::DOM::Twig

0.03  Fri Jan 7 2005
	- improved test coverage
	- clarified and documented new behaviour of text elements

0.04  Wed Feb 2 2005
	- fixed errors in documentation
	- doubled the number of tests
	- fixed createDocument to attach root element to document element
0.05 Wed Mar 30 2005
	- no longer requires XML::Xerces::DOMDocument in getElementwithText
